Body: WEBSITE   â€¢   WHITEPAPER   â€¢   TELEGRAM   â€¢   TWITTER   â€¢   MEDIUM    What do we do?   Paytomat is a platform to incentivize transactional usage of crypto through a decentralized network of point-of-sale terminals.  We have built an extension to receive payments in crypto on existing POS (point- of-sale) solutions and successfully deployed it on 150 merchants We are now beta-testing customer mobile wallets and a standalone Paytomat Mobile POS for both payment processing and a blockchain-based loyalty program  The Paytomat business is structured as a decentralized autonomous organization, incorporating elements of the decentralized franchise To augment its decentralization, our engineers have developed the Point-of-Sale as Proof-of-Stake (POS as PoS) protocol, allowing any POS device in our network to become a masternode on PTM Blockchain          Content Creation Campaign   We are going to announce the campaign to cooperate with those interested in our concept and our project. Hope the mobile wallet is ready for release soon, to have a good look at it. I am not calling it a scam, but it raises serious questions that need addressing before investing.
